{"tid":289842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞刀匪闖旺角賓館　逼大陸仔過680萬人民幣","createTime":"2017-06-19T10:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T11:13:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8b7a0c101d303d1c720eda2165cf8bfadbc9e4","tid":289842,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"旺角發生賓館劫案，下午近2時，2名內地男子被2名男子帶上在洗衣街215號一間賓館內，期間，3名南亞漢與另一男子闖入賓館，持刀威逼其中2名內地男子，轉帳680萬元人民幣(約780萬港元)到指定銀行戶口。 <br />\n<br />\n6名匪徒之後逃去無蹤，事主自行到旺角警署報案，報稱遭人行劫。警方正追緝3名中國籍男子及3名南亞漢下落，旺角警區助理指揮官(刑事)鍾志明與多名探員接報趕抵賓館，翻查附近「天眼」作進一步調查。下午4時許，探員拖篋進入現場調查。"},{"pid":"d85ef30f0e2521607c770afe0f80f72778227ceb","tid":289842,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418ca231ca643be72c87a37af3b98c8cc7f55635","tid":289842,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e78aa759e95a01696f56ffcadcc4ed47eb6af6","tid":289842,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"dog bite dog, good good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5911d3c518ee89dd4267039dc88083edc8601a59","tid":289842,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}